| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4057 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 65bd9b9a-e5de-5c5a-9e47-a6f9df2fee61"
